.-help for ^xtile2^.-^xtile2^ creates a new variable that categorizes exp by its subgroup        quantiles.-----------------------------------------------------------------------  ^xtile2^ newvar ^=^ exp [weight] [^if^ exp] [^in^ range]    ^,^ by(varlist) [ ^n^quantiles^(^#^)^  ^alt^def ]Options--------  ^nquantiles(^#^)^ specifies the number of quantiles.      ^by(varlist)^ specifies subgroups within which the category will begenerated.Examples---------  . ^xtile2 quart = bp if age>=25, nq(4) by(sex race)^   Also see---------  Manual:  ^[R] pctile^Author-------  Zhiqiang Wang  Menzies School of Health Research  Darwin, Australia  wang@@menzies.su.edu.au  